<H3> <TI>   Visits Havana Hospital </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Visits Havana Hospital </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   FL0906225294 Havana Radio Reloj Network in Spanish 1939 GMT 
9 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> FL0906225294 </F>
<F P=104>  Havana Radio Reloj Network </F>
<F P=105>  Spanish </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] On 9 June, the CPC delegation headed by Politburo 
member Wu Bangguo, secretary of the CPC in Shanghai, visited the 
Hermanos Ameijeiras Clinical Surgical Hospital in Havana. Public 
Health Minister Dr. Julio Teja and hospital director Dr. Raul 
Cabrera briefed the visitors on all aspects of the Cuban medical 
system. 
  Previously, the CPC delegation had seen a video covering the 
work done at the hospital. The hospital has 52 consulting rooms 
for diverse medical specialities to care for the population, 
mainly from Centro Habana and Habana Vieja. Later on, the CPC 
delegation visited various areas of the hospital and expressed 
interest in other aspects of Cuban medicine. 

</TEXT>

