<H3> <TI>   Wasmosy to Montevideo, To Sign Dredging Channel Pact </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Wasmosy to Montevideo, To Sign Dredging Channel Pact </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   PY1006183394 Asuncion Cerro Cora Sistema Nacional de 
