<H3> <TI>   Havana Reports Pilot Defection to Key West </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Havana Reports Pilot Defection to Key West </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   FL1306212994 Havana Radio Reloj Network in Spanish 1942 GMT 
13 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> FL1306212994 </F>
<F P=104>  Havana Radio Reloj Network </F>
<F P=105>  Spanish </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] The following is a communique from the Civil 
Aeronautics Institute: Arriel Corral Gonzalez, pilot, defected 
yesterday, 12 June. Corral, who worked for the National Air 
Services Enterprise, took an AN-2 [as heard] type airplane that 
was being used for agricultural work in Pinar del Rio. The 
traitor flew the plane to the Boca Chica Naval Air Station in 
Key West, United States. Cuba is currently taking steps to have 
the plane returned. 

</TEXT>

