<H3> <TI>   Politburo Member Machado Attends Guantanamo Assembly </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Politburo Member Machado Attends Guantanamo Assembly </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   FL1106110094 Havana Tele Rebelde and Cuba Vision Networks in 
Spanish 0000 GMT 11 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> FL1106110094 </F>
<F P=104>  Havana Tele Rebelde and Cuba Vision Networks </F>
<F P=105>  Spanish </F>


