in Spanish 1300 GMT 13 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> PA1306151794 </F>
<F P=104>  Mexico City Canal 13 Television Azteca Network 
in Spanish 1300 GMT 13 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=105> Spanish </F>


<TEXT>
